arStrings.szText: Had to chase away another Zakarum missionary today. They visit here, ply the children with sweets to wash the taste of ashes out of their mouths.
I’ve seen what their light brings. The Zakarum's fervor drove them to burn down my village.
I know there’s a ledger there of what happened. I want to... I need to find it. I could show the children and the town why we must never let in the missionaries.
Can you take me there and help me recover the ledger?
